nM for the NBD in the KCl-containing buffer [Fig.
1(A)]. Next, we purified the NBD in the NaCl-containing buffer and crystallized the ADP- and Mg2þ ion-bound NBD without Kþ ion. A 1.65 A˚ native
data set was collected, and the initial phase was
